{"title":"报喜——记绥远农村","authors":["泾水生"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"报喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——记绥远农村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白窗户，红花花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂给哥哥缝冬袜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千针腰儿万针底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"针针穿着心里话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左只绣个“英雄人”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右只绣上“打到底”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们的日子苦到头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东当了咱主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里路上捎个信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺给哥哥报大喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不说黄牛吃的胖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不提庄稼长的强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此人民当了家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新中国开朵大金花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盼望哥哥捉蒋贼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺和嫂嫂生产忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泾水生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十、十三、"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}